headline: PNC earnings, Fedspeak, homebuilder confidence: What to Watch
summary: Market Domination Overtime Host Josh Lipton previews several of the biggest stories to come tomorrow, Friday, January 16, including earnings results from regional bank PNC Financial Services (PNC), commentary from several top Federal Reserve officials, and the latest reading on US homebuilder confidence. To watch more expert insights and analysis on the latest market action, check out more Market Domination Overtime.
